         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Office of Lands and Survey, ¶ Melbourne, 4th September 1867. ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ Adverting to the notification in the Government Gazette of the 27th ultimo, ¶ Victoria Government Gazette, 27 August 1867, p. 1...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">67.09.04a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From John Lewis</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Unit 2, p. 520, VPRS 7936/P1 outward letterbooks of the Secretary for Lands, VA 538 Department of Crown Lands and Survey, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Office of Lands and Survey,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, 4th September 1867.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Adverting to the notification in the Government Gazette of the 27th ultimo,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Victoria Government Gazette</seg>, 27 August 1867, p. 1595. The notice announced the appointment of M,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Surveyor General (Charles Ligar),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Assistant Commissioner of Lands and Survey (Clement Hodgkinson),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Inspector General of Public Works (William Wardell),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Secretary of Mines (Robert Brough Smyth),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Chief Mining Surveyor (Thomas Couchman)<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to a Board of Inquiry regarding the State Forests of Victoria.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of the appointment by His Excellency The Governor in Council of a Board of inquiry regarding the State Forests of Victoria, I am requested to invite your attendance at a meeting of the Board to be held in the Board rooms at this office on Thursday next the 5th instant, at 2 p.m.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient Servant,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>John Lewis<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The same letter was sent to all members of the Board of Inquiry.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
